						<sci:value>Retrieves Foundation Hub entities</sci:value>
						<sci:value>&lt;p&gt;Retrieves data records from the Hub using the set of APIs and modifiers detailed in the  Foundation Hub API Documentation.  
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
This is available from: http://hubserver:port/foundation/hub/apidoc&lt;/p&gt;
</sci:value>
