							</sci:arg>
							<sci:arg name="ComponentHelp" type="StringType" required="false" visibility="nevershow" multi="true">
								<sci:value>100</sci:value>
								<sci:value>Ensures that the layout of a report is maintained when collapsing components to a subprotocol</sci:value>
								<sci:value>Used in a subprotocol for directing records from Pass ports of components in the subprotocol, to the Pass port of the subprotocol that is connected to a Reporting component.  This component ensures that the layout of a report is maintained when components upstream of a Reporting component are collapsed into a subprotocol.  This component is automatically added, if necessary, when a subprotocol is created.</sci:value>
								<sci:value>Generic</sci:value>
