						<sci:value>&lt;p&gt;This component accepts reporting objects as input (e.g., tables, text and images), and displays the output as an HTML file in your default web browser.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Notes:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

